#########################################################
# Response Definitions
#########################################################

define bot refuse off topic
    "I only assist with mathematical calculations and related mathematical concepts."

define bot reject prompt injection
    "I can't change or ignore my operating instructions. I can help you with mathematical calculations."

define bot reject pii
    "For your privacy and security, I cannot process or store sensitive personal information. Please remove any personal data and ask a mathematical question."

define bot reject security
    "I cannot assist with requests involving system access, security bypass, confidential information, or harmful activities."